00:01:42,300 --> 00:01:46,550
派拉蒙新闻为您带来安公主出访伦敦的专题报道
Paramount News brings you a special coverage of Princess Ann's visit to London,

28
00:01:46,640 --> 00:01:51,060
这是她在欧洲各国首都进行友好宣传的第一站
the first stop on her much-publicized goodwill tour of European capitals.

29
00:01:51,680 --> 00:01:53,560
她受到英国皇室级别的隆重欢迎
She gets a royal welcome from the British,

30
00:01:53,640 --> 00:01:58,690
这位欧洲最古老皇族之一的高贵年轻成员受到数千民众的热烈欢呼
as thousands cheer the gracious young member of one of Europe's oldest ruling families.

31
00:01:59,150 --> 00:02:03,440
在为期3天的宣传活动结束后 她参观了白金汉宫
After three days of continuous activity and a visit to Buckingham Palace,

32
00:02:03,530 --> 00:02:05,400
安飞抵阿姆斯特丹
Ann flew to Amsterdam,

33
00:02:05,490 --> 00:02:08,820
在那里 公主殿下为新的国际援助大厦奠基
where Her Royal Highness dedicated the new International Aid Building

34
00:02:08,860 --> 00:02:10,950
并出席了一艘邮轮的命名仪式
and christened an ocean liner,

35
00:02:11,030 --> 00:02:12,490
之后前往巴黎
then went to Paris,

36
00:02:12,530 --> 00:02:14,580
出席多项官方活动
where she attended many official functions

37
00:02:14,660 --> 00:02:19,580
旨在加强同西欧各国的贸易关系
designed to cement trade relations between her country and the Western European nations.

38
00:02:20,370 --> 00:02:23,000
现在终于 来到了不朽之城 罗马
And so, to Rome, the Eternal City,

39
00:02:23,040 --> 00:02:26,960
为迎接公主的到来 罗马举行了盛大的阅兵式
where the princess' visit was marked by a spectacular military parade

40
00:02:27,050 --> 00:02:30,260
突击步兵团乐队的演奏将阅兵式推向了高潮
highlighted by the band of the crack Bersaglieri regiment.

41
00:02:36,060 --> 00:02:41,390
从年轻的公主的微笑中你丝毫看不出持续一周公共场合露面的疲惫感
The smiling young princess showed no sign of the strain of the week's continuous public appearances,

42
00:02:41,480 --> 00:02:43,480
当晚 在该国大使馆
and, at her country's embassy that evening,

43
00:02:43,560 --> 00:02:49,820
该国驻意大利大使为她特设晚宴并举行了舞会
a formal reception and ball in her honor was given by her country's ambassador to Italy.

44
00:03:08,130 --> 00:03:09,880
公主殿下
Her Royal Highness.

45
00:04:05,640 --> 00:04:10,270
罗马教廷大使 奥托蒙特阁下
His Excellency, the Papal Nuncio, Monsignor Altomonte.

46
00:04:16,860 --> 00:04:19,780
雨果 梅西 德 法明顿爵士
Sir Hugo Macy de Farmington.

47
00:04:19,860 --> 00:04:23,610
- 晚上好 雨果爵士
- 晚上好 公主殿下
- Good evening, Sir Hugo.
- Good evening, Your Royal Highness.

48
00:04:23,860 --> 00:04:26,780
