58
00:05:08,700 --> 00:05:10,610
晚上好 伯爵夫人
Good evening, Countess.

59
00:05:12,200 --> 00:05:13,660
晚上好
Good evening.

60
00:05:19,040 --> 00:05:22,170
诺 德 卡莫斯爵士及夫人
Señor e Señora Joao de Camoes.

61
00:05:22,920 --> 00:05:24,380
晚上好
Good evening.

62
00:05:27,960 --> 00:05:30,260
哈桑 EL 丁 帕夏
Hassan El Din Pasha.

63
00:05:31,380 --> 00:05:32,880
您好
How do you do?

64
00:07:20,070 --> 00:07:21,940
我不喜欢这件睡袍
I hate this nightgown.

65
00:07:22,690 --> 00:07:26,700
我不喜欢我所有的睡袍 还有 我也不喜欢我所有的内衣
I hate all my nightgowns, and I hate all my underwear, too.

66
00:07:26,780 --> 00:07:29,030
亲爱的 你的东西都很漂亮
My dear, you have lovely things.

67
00:07:29,120 --> 00:07:31,410
可我还没有200岁那么老
But I'm not two hundred years old.

68
00:07:32,160 --> 00:07:33,950
为什么我就不能穿着睡衣睡觉？
Why can't I sleep in pajamas?

69
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:35,250
睡衣！
Pajamas!

70
00:07:35,330 --> 00:07:37,000
只要上衣
Just the top part.

71
00:07:39,790 --> 00:07:43,880
