Did you know there are people who sleep with absolutely nothing on at all?

72
00:07:44,500 --> 00:07:46,880
我得很高兴的说我不知道有这种事
I rejoice to say that I did not.

73
00:07:49,590 --> 00:07:50,800
听啊
Listen.

74
00:07:57,140 --> 00:07:58,890
安 你的拖鞋
Ann, your slippers.

75
