94
00:08:55,860 --> 00:08:57,950
你要出席放置奠基石的仪式
You will preside over the laying of the cornerstone.

95
00:08:58,030 --> 00:08:59,320
讲话的内容同上周一是一样的
Same speech as last Monday.

96
00:08:59,410 --> 00:09:00,660
贸易关系
Trade relations.

97
00:09:00,740 --> 00:09:01,830
是的
Yes.

98
00:09:02,780 --> 00:09:04,410
在孤儿院说这个吗？
For the orphans?

99
00:09:05,040 --> 00:09:06,960
不 不 不对 是另一个讲话
No, no, no, the other one.

100
00:09:07,040 --> 00:09:08,460
年轻与发展
Youth and progress.

101
00:09:08,540 --> 00:09:09,870
就是这个
Precisely.

102
00:09:10,210 --> 00:09:12,960
11:45 回到这里休息 不 不对
11:45, back here to rest. No, that's wrong.

103
00:09:13,040 --> 00:09:15,710
11:45 回这里召开记者招待会
11:45, conference here with the press.

104
00:09:15,800 --> 00:09:17,260
甜美与庄重
Sweetness and decency.

105
00:09:17,340 --> 00:09:20,220
1:00 同外交部用午餐
1:00 sharp, lunch with the Foreign Ministry.

106
00:09:20,300 --> 00:09:22,890
你要系上白色的花边并配上一束
You will wear your white lace and carry a bouquet of

107
00:09:22,970 --> 00:09:25,390
- 非常小的粉玫瑰
- 非常小的粉玫瑰
- very small pink roses.
- Very small pink roses.

108
00:09:26,600 --> 00:09:28,890
3:05 匾额赠送仪式
3:05, presentation of a plaque.

109
00:09:28,980 --> 00:09:29,980
谢谢
Thank you.

110
00:09:30,060 --> 00:09:32,730
4:10 检阅宪兵特勤卫队...
4:10, review Special Guard of Carabinieri...

111
00:09:32,810 --> 00:09:33,860
我不能收 谢谢
No, thank you.

112
00:09:33,900 --> 00:09:36,270
- 4:45 回到这里换...
- 您好 真迷人
- 4:45, back here to change...
- How do you do? Charmed.

113
00:09:36,360 --> 00:09:38,230
- ...上您的制服会见...
- 很高兴...
- ...into your uniform to meet the...
- So happy...

114
00:09:38,320 --> 00:09:39,440
别说了！
Stop!

115
00:09:40,190 --> 00:09:42,570
- 我的上帝啊！
- 别说了！别说了！别说了！
- Good heavens!
- Stop! Stop! Stop!

116
00:09:44,280 --> 00:09:46,070
没事 亲爱的 没洒出来
It's all right, dear. It didn't spill.

117
00:09:46,120 --> 00:09:48,280
我才不在乎它洒没洒
I don't care if it spilled or not.

118
00:09:48,370 --> 00:09:50,200
就算我淹死在里边我也不在乎！
I don't care if I drowned in it!

119
00:09:50,290 --> 00:09:52,660
亲爱的 你病了
My dear, you're ill.

120
00:09:54,000 --> 00:09:55,830
我派人去把博纳科温医生请来
I'll send for Dr. Bonnachoven.

121
00:09:55,920 --> 00:09:59,340
我不要博纳科温医生！就让我安静的死掉吧
I don't want Dr. Bonnachoven! Please let me die in peace.

122
00:09:59,420 --> 00:10:00,420
你不会死的
You're not dying.

123
00:10:00,500 --> 00:10:01,800
别管我！
Leave me!

124
00:10:02,630 --> 00:10:05,630
- 别管我！
- 你就是有些紧张了 控制你的情绪 安
- Leave me!
- It's nerves. Control yourself, Ann.

125
00:10:05,720 --> 00:10:07,800
我不要！
I don't want to!

126
00:10:07,890 --> 00:10:09,390
公主殿下！
Your Highness!

127
00:10:11,350 --> 00:10:12,600
我去把博纳科温医生找来
I'll get Dr. Bonnachoven.

128
00:10:12,640 --> 00:10:14,100
这没用的
It's no use.

129
00:10:14,640 --> 00:10:17,100
在他赶到这里前我就会死掉
I'll be dead before he gets here.

130
00:10:26,110 --> 00:10:27,150
她已经睡着了
She's asleep.

131
00:10:27,240 --> 00:10:30,320
3分钟前她还是歇斯底里的 医生
She was in hysterics three minutes ago, Doctor.

132
00:10:33,370 --> 00:10:34,410
您睡着了吗 殿下？
Are you asleep, ma'am?

133
00:10:34,490 --> 00:10:35,540
没有！
No!

134
00:10:38,540 --> 00:10:41,420
我只打扰您一小会儿 公主殿下
I'll only disturb Your Royal Highness a moment.

135
00:10:41,500 --> 00:10:44,170
我真的很惭愧 博纳科温医生
I'm very ashamed, Dr. Bonnachoven.

136
00:10:44,250 --> 00:10:46,170
突然间 我就哭起来了
Sudenly, I was crying.

137
00:10:47,630 --> 00:10:50,220
哭 是再平常不过的事了
To cry, a perfectly normal thing to do.

138
00:10:50,300 --> 00:10:53,930
最重要的是让她在出席记者招待会的时候能够冷静 放松 医生
It's most important she be calm and relaxed for the press conference, Doctor.

139
00:10:54,010 --> 00:10:55,810
别担心 医生
Don't worry, Doctor.

140
00:10:55,890 --> 00:10:57,640
我会冷静 放松的
I'll be calm and relaxed.

141
00:10:57,720 --> 00:10:59,810
我会欠身 微笑的
I'll bow, and I'll smile.

142
00:10:59,890 --> 00:11:02,390
我会改善贸易关系 还有...
I'll improve trade relations, and...

143
00:11:02,850 --> 00:11:05,690
她又这样了 给她点儿什么药 医生 快点
There she goes again. Give her something, Doctor, please.

144
00:11:05,770 --> 00:11:07,400
请把她的衣袖卷起来
<font color=#FF7F00>[请注意将军的表演]</font>
Uncover her arm, please.

145
00:11:11,610 --> 00:11:12,610
那是什么？
What's that?

146
00:11:12,700 --> 00:11:14,160
镇定促睡眠的药
Sleep and calm.

147
00:11:14,240 --> 00:11:18,080
这会让公主殿下您感到放松并感到些许愉快的
This will relax you and make Your Highness feel a little happy.

148
00:11:18,160 --> 00:11:20,490
这是一种新药 没有任何副作用
It's a new drug, quite harmless.

149
00:11:24,290 --> 00:11:25,500
好了
There.

150
00:11:27,000 --> 00:11:29,130
我没感觉有什么不同
I don't feel any different.

151
00:11:29,290 --> 00:11:32,510
你会的 要过一阵才会起效
You will. It may take a little time to take hold.

152
00:11:33,090 --> 00:11:34,880
现在 快躺下吧
Just, now, lie back.

